  <description>
    <p>VertexWrite is a lightweight GTK Markdown editor for opening, editing, previewing, and organizing documents wherever they live: local folders or remote servers over SSH/SFTP.</p>
    <p>It focuses on fast startup, clean reading, live split preview, and a sidebar that browses local and remote file trees without becoming a full notes database.</p>
  </description>
